ValidationReport structure:
```typescript
interface ValidationReport {
  proposedRule: string;
  verdict: 'accept' | 'reject' | 'unclear';
  confidence: number;  // 0-1
  evidence: Evidence[];
  reason: string;
  stats: {
    sessionsScanned: number;
    supporting: number;
    contradicting: number;
