Output format:
```
PROPOSED RULE: "{proposedRule}"

VERDICT: {✓ ACCEPT | ✗ REJECT | ? UNCLEAR} (confidence: {0.XX})

EVIDENCE:
- [{classification}] {sessionPath}
  "{excerpt}"
  {timestamp}
{... more evidence ...}

REASON: {reason}

STATISTICS:
- Sessions scanned: {N}
- Supporting: {N}
- Contradicting: {N}
- Neutral: {N}
```

Formatting rules:
- Verdict symbols: ✓ (accept), ✗ (reject), ? (unclear)
- Confidence as 2 decimal places
- Truncate session paths to last 2 components if verbose=false
- Show max 5 evidence items unless verbose=true
- Color coding (if terminal supports):
  - Green for accept/supports
  - Red for reject/contradicts
  - Yellow for unclear/neutral

